data.description: Fantastic four-bedroom, three-bathroom home with a great room plan and fenced yard, conveniently located near the Suncoast Parkway for easy access to miles of bike trails and Tampa and its surrounding areas.  The updated kitchen has 42" wood cabinets, GRANITE countertops with backsplash, a breakfast nook, tile flooring, a snack bar, a step-in pantry, and recessed lighting. Great room plan with formal dining is perfect for any family, decorator fans, and 5" baseboard molding with access to the covered backyard patio. The large primary bathroom has a garden tub, a new glass door shower, double-sink vanity with granite counters, a walk-in closet, and luxury vinyl flooring. Bedrooms two and three are connected with a full bathroom. With a fourth bedroom and full bath with tub/shower located off of the formal dining area! Entertain on the expanded patio with a fenced yard. Interior laundry. Existing appliances will not be conveyed; BRAND NEW GE stainless steel appliances will be installed before closing.
